			[1508] heading 'Intro'
			[1510] paragraph ''
				StaticText 'tRPC allows you to easily build & consume fully typesafe APIs without schemas or code generation.'
			[1511] heading 'Features'
			[1513] list ''
				[1514] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText '‚úÖ'
					StaticText 'Well-tested and production ready.'
				[1515] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText 'üßô\u200d‚ôÇÔ∏è\xa0 Full static typesafety & autocompletion on the client, for inputs, outputs, and errors.'
				[1516] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText 'üêé'
					StaticText 'Snappy DX - No code generation, run-time bloat, or build pipeline.'
				[1517] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText 'üçÉ'
					StaticText 'Light - tRPC has zero deps and a tiny client-side footprint.'
				[1518] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText 'üêª'
					StaticText 'Easy to add to your existing brownfield project.'
				[1519] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText 'üîã'
					StaticText 'Batteries included - React.js/Next.js/Express.js/Fastify adapters.'
					[1520] emphasis ''
						StaticText '(But tRPC is not tied to React, and there are many'
						[1521] link 'community adapters', url='https://trpc.io/docs/awesome-trpc#-extensions--community-add-ons'
						StaticText 'for other libraries)'
				[1522] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText 'ü•É'
					StaticText 'Subscriptions support.'
				[1523] listitem ''
					ListMarker '‚Ä¢'
					StaticText '‚ö°'
					StaticText 'Ô∏è\xa0 Request batching - requests made at the same time can be automatically combined into one'
